channel.title: SageScape 667 - New sick RSPS
channel.description:
SageScape is a new 667 rsps, based off of fun, variety, and things you wouldn't see in any other server. We strive to be the most unique server out there. Although we have just now started opening our doors to the public we are still in heavy development. We will be up 24/7 unless down for maintenance. Any suggestions and/or comments about how the server is going or how you would like to see it changed would be greatly appreciated. Also all donations are currently doubled.
Stable!!!!
Brand New!
Chill staff!
Constant updates!
Custom bosses released every week!
We will have raids!
Currently looking for staff!
Download Client: https://www.dropbox.com/s/q91xfrpw28...Scape.jar?dl=0
Have fun.
